The app has no `helmet()` for default security headers, no CORS policy, no rate limiting, and no request size limits. These aren't bugs in 22 lines, but they're the defaults you want before this app does anything real:
```js
const helmet = require('helmet');
const rateLimit = require('express-rate-limit');
app.use(helmet());
app.use(express.json({ limit: '100kb' }));
app.use(rateLimit({ windowMs: 60_000, max: 100 }));
