| P0 | Add authentication middleware before any data-returning endpoint |
| P1 | Add rate limiting and a central error handler |
| P1 | Introduce input validation scaffolding (`zod` / `joi`) |
| P2 | Add structured logging with secret redaction |
| P2 | CORS policy, graceful shutdown, `process.env.PORT` |
