app.use(cors({ origin: ['https://your-frontend.example.com'], methods: ['GET'] }));
```

#### 3. A04 — Insecure Design: no rate limiting (Low–Medium)
Both endpoints are unauthenticated and will happily serve unlimited traffic — trivial DoS / scraping vector.

**Recommendation:**
```js
