`app.listen(3000)` serves plaintext HTTP. If deployed directly rather than behind a TLS-terminating proxy, credentials and PII travel in cleartext. Ensure deployment runs behind nginx/ALB/Cloudflare with TLS, and add HSTS (provided by `helmet()` above).

