app.disable('x-powered-by');
```

**Line 18:** `app.listen(3000, ...)` — port is hardcoded. Use `process.env.PORT || 3000` so it works behind managed hosts, and bind explicitly (`app.listen(port, '0.0.0.0', ...)` only when intended).

