```

### 4. No structured error handling (Low — OWASP A09)
There is no error-handling middleware. If the app grows and a handler throws, Express's default handler can leak stack traces in development mode.

```js
app.use((err, req, res, next) => {
  console.error(err);                  // log server-side
  res.status(500).json({ error: 'Internal Server Error' });
});
```

