`app.listen(3000, …)` ignores `process.env.PORT` and has no `SIGTERM` handler, so in-flight requests can be cut off (minor integrity concern; also makes zero-downtime deploys harder, which indirectly affects security patch rollout).

**Recommendation:**
```js
