3. **Hardcoded listen host** — `app.listen(3000, ...)` binds to all interfaces by default. In containerized/production environments prefer an explicit host (`'127.0.0.1'` behind a reverse proxy) and port from env (`process.env.PORT`).

4. **PII in `/users`** — Email addresses are returned to any unauthenticated caller. There's no auth/authz middleware. If this endpoint is ever real, it needs authentication and likely a filtered projection (no emails for unauthorized users).

